What is the median grams of sugarsper shelf and the number of cereals per shelf, when we drop the missing values (coded as sugars = -1)?

The person with the nearest birthday: explain out loud to your neighbor how you would do this manipulation.



cereal |&gt; 
  select(sugars, shelf) |&gt; 
  filter(sugars != -1) |&gt; 
  group_by(shelf) |&gt; 
  summarise(med_sugars = median(sugars),
            num_shelf = n())

